{"tid":1042844,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"好想搵番一隻GBA嘅game","createTime":"2019-03-01T21:30:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-01T23:07:19.000Z","uid":95075,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"e7a8218dc17533a02863d1eab66c6a240f1c7cd1","tid":1042844,"uid":95075,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-01T21:30:41.000Z","msg":"細個好鐘意玩一隻GBA嘅game，但係唔記得左個名，呢<br />\n幾年嘗試過google都搵唔番，應該係因為記憶太零碎。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我記得係konami出嘅冒險類game，主角係個有翼嘅𡃁仔，如果打啲怪獸就會將佢地變成正方形/圓形，可以掟出去或者用黎借力飛高啲。印象中有八個世界咁，後期要用少少腦先過到關。有無巴打知係咩game？"},{"pid":"58d8fd81454bd7bbb3b26f2b120004a2dac93c24","tid":1042844,"uid":51684,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-01T21:39:33.000Z","msg":"星之卡比?"},{"pid":"7f919dc275907cc35a0d142b5b6ce3d9c05f8f07","tid":1042844,"uid":16976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-01T21:42:00.000Z","msg":"風之古洛羅亞"},{"pid":"357ac780b29d9084cec02f5bfdf52c45525e6edc","tid":1042844,"uid":182203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-01T21:42:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/03/02/054156_0ff8bebbf1123e70c6c3e3613681e253.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F03%2F02%2F054156_0ff8bebbf1123e70c6c3e3613681e253.png&h=14a2b8d6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nthis one?"},{"pid":"fe850c7b273d09c25f797918376b9d8bf14d4533","tid":1042844,"uid":196924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-01T23:07:19.000Z","msg":"印象中Konami冇呢類game<br />\n你話Namco就有啲機"}]}